---
import { GraduationCap, Sparkles, Workflow } from "lucide-astro";
---

<section id="about" class="section-pad relative overflow-hidden" data-section>
  <div class="site-shell grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] lg:items-end">
    <div>
      <p class="section-kicker" data-animate>About</p>
      <h2 class="mt-6 max-w-xl text-balance text-4xl font-black leading-tight tracking-[0] text-white sm:text-5xl" data-animate>
        A practical builder with a sharp academic foundation.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-5">
      <p class="text-pretty text-lg leading-8 text-white/72" data-animate>
        Mohammad Al Amin is a Computer Science student at Islamic University of Madinah and a Web Developer at Artemesis Company. His work sits at the useful intersection of elegant interfaces, reliable backend systems, mobile products, and intelligent automation.
      </p>
      <p class="text-pretty text-lg leading-8 text-white/62" data-animate>
        He builds websites, web applications, mobile apps, and automation systems with a clean engineering mindset: responsive experiences, maintainable components, and details that make a product feel international.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="site-shell mt-12 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
    <article class="glass-panel rounded-[1.35rem] p-6" data-animate>
      <GraduationCap class="mb-6 text-[#32f5c8]" size={30} strokeWidth={1.8} />
      <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white">CS Student</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-white/62">Studying Computer Science at Islamic University of Madinah.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="glass-panel rounded-[1.35rem] p-6" data-animate>
      <Workflow class="mb-6 text-[#59d7ff]" size={30} strokeWidth={1.8} />
      <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white">Product Engineer</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-white/62">Building web, mobile, and automation systems at Artemesis Company.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="glass-panel rounded-[1.35rem] p-6" data-animate>
      <Sparkles class="mb-6 text-[#d9aa59]" size={30} strokeWidth={1.8} />
      <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white">Premium UI Focus</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-white/62">Designing modern responsive interfaces with clean motion and strong detail.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
